These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  teacher, software-developer, musician, freelancer, pilot, dressmaker, lawyer
There are 7 different nationalities: german, japanese, egyptian, indonesian, dutch, british, russian
 1. the freelancer is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the dutch is the freelancer##1
 3. the lawyer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the british##1
 5. the musician is in the middle##1
 6. the german is on the far left##1
 7. the pilot is the german##1
 8. the teacher is on the right of the british##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the japanese##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the musician##1
11. the lawyer is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | pilot | freelancer | software-developer | musician | teacher | dressmaker | lawyer |
| Nationality   | german    | dutch   | indonesian      | british | egyptian    | japanese    | russian         |

