.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pineapple, radish, blueberry, pumpkin, apple, cherry, cauliflower
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, techno, house, metal, country, r&b, hip-hop
 1. the fan of country is the person eating pumpkin##1
 2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | pineapple | radish | apple | pumpkin | cherry | cauliflower | blueberry |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | house   | metal   | country      | jazz       | hip-hop       | r&b     |

