.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: strawberry, mango, cabbage, pumpkin, watermelon, broccoli, plum
The people have 7 different jobs:  videographer, manager, analyst, electrician, entrepreneur, librarian, nurse
 1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the manager is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the videographer is the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the analyst is on the right of the manager##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the analyst##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the electrician##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the electrician##1
10. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the videographer##1
11. the electrician is in the middle##1
12. the person eating plum is on the left of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | mango | watermelon     | cabbage  | broccoli       | strawberry       | plum  | pumpkin   |
| Job    | librarian  | videographer | nurse | electrician | manager | analyst | entrepreneur |

