.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, punk, d&b, electronic, salsa, ambient, dubstep
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, turkish, pakistani, colombian, french, chinese, british
 1. the fan of salsa is the turkish##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the chinese is on the right of the pakistani##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
 7. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the chinese##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the french##1
10. the french is on the left of the fan of punk##1
11. the british is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | dubstep     | electronic     | d&b      | punk | salsa      | funk     |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani | chinese | french | british | turkish | polish |

