.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, collecting, woodworking, photography, puzzles, card-games, rock-climbing
7 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, chinchilla, rabbit, pony, ferret, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the owner of the pony is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | collecting | woodworking | card-games     | photography | rock-climbing | puzzles | singing |
| Pet     | turtle   | chinchilla    | pony | ferret     | goat         | rabbit     | mouse        |

