.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, mirinda, milk, water, hot-chocolate, fanta
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, boat, motorbike, van, scooter, airplane, train
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | hot-chocolate   | cola | milk | fanta  | water | tea |
| Transport   | van   | scooter | taxi | airplane     | boat | train | motorbike   |

