 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person driving the bike is the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | zombie | action | mystery | family     | musical | epic |
| Transport     | helicopter | airplane      | taxi | tram    | train | quad-bike   | bike  |

